productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
one of my hobbies is skydiving. and when i'm skydiving this works great.
I tried to nab it but got biscuit all over it.
My peacock loves to play with it.
